{
  "stem": "4113.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we got there and came back to our home, our store, the order came from the Gestapo, who had their headquarters across the street from us, that all Jews are to load up and go east on the other side of the San River, because, if you may remember, there was that secret agreement between Hitler and Stalin that they will divide Poland into two.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That border was only 40 kilometers, approximately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The San River was the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jews have to go there, so as to go to the Soviets, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we again took Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Socha and we put our stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we were loading, a Gestapo man comes down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Becker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He comes down, says, no, [GERMAN], which means glazier master, you cannot go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We need you here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we unloaded and we stayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, we were considered important to the economy, because you must know, there was lots of traffic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were broken windows everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their car windows were smashed, many of them, that had to be glazed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to be fixed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were considered important for the economy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed and they left us alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took the-- the warehouse away and shipped it off to Germany, most of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then they appointed a treuhander, which is a supervisor, to run the show.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were just working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were very busy, really, very busy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German soldiers were continually coming in to our store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- the Gestapo used to come in to frame all their diplomas and all their things that they had that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can even remember the words that Schmatzler, who was Haupsturmfuhrer Schmatzler, who was the head of the Gestapo in our town, got this recognition from Hitler.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
